<note n="0056002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0056002">本文 coditvā 為 codetvā？</note>
<note n="0057003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0057003">勒棄多赴婆那婆私（Vanavāsa）（大王統史十二．四參照）。</note>
<note n="0057004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0057004">在他傳 Dundubhissara 為妙聲大鼓主，音譯，純毘帝須。</note>
